# Progress Installation

You can [install Progress package](https://www.nuget.org/packages/Skclusive.Material.Progress/) by typing the below command in your terminal:

```csharp
dotnet add package Skclusive.Material.Progress
```

Then, you can import it in your `_Imports.razor`.

```csharp
@using Skclusive.Material.Progress
```

Then, you can render the style for this component it in your `Router.razor`.

```html
<ProgressStyles />
```

